Day Night Medias:
A fully responsive photo gallery website created for a company called Day Night Medias.
This website was built to showcase some of the company's work.
This includes an image gallery that uses a grid system. The grid is fully responsive and changes in size as the screen size changes.
Inculdes a navigation menu as the screen size reduces.
Includes a text link button, that changes color when hovered over and redirects to the company's Instagram page in a new tab when clicked.
Also includes one of the company's embed Youtube video, with controls such as play, pause, full screen, share and a link to the Youtube Page for the video.
